thor/Wang Shuhong","line":128},{"title":"Author/Yi Du","target":"Author/Yi Du","line":129},{"title":"Author/Du Yi","target":"Author/Du Yi","line":130},{"title":"Author/Yu Ruirui","target":"Author/Yu Ruirui","line":131},{"title":"Author/Yu Ruirui","target":"Author/Yu Ruirui","line":132},{"title":"Author/Yi Peng","target":"Author/Yi Peng","line":133},{"title":"Author/Yi Peng","target":"Author/Yi Peng","line":134},{"title":"Author/Yifan Song","target":"Author/Yifan Song","line":135},{"title":"Author/Song Yifan","target":"Author/Song Yifan","line":136},{"title":"Author/Yun-Shi Zhi","target":"Author/Yun-Shi Zhi","line":137},{"title":"Author/Zhi Yunshi","target":"Author/Zhi Yunshi","line":138},{"title":"Author/Xun Song","target":"Author/Xun Song","line":139},{"title":"Author/Song Xun","target":"Author/Song Xun","line":140},{"title":"Author/Yaping Guo","target":"Author/Yaping Guo","line":141},{"title":"Author/Guo Yaping","target":"Author/Guo Yaping","line":142},{"title":"Author/Zhendan He","target":"Author/Zhendan He","line":143},{"title":"Author/He Zhendan","target":"Author/He Zhendan","line":144},{"title":"Author/Tie Chen","target":"Author/Tie Chen","line":145},{"title":"Author/Chen Tie","target":"Author/Chen Tie","line":146},{"title":"Author/Chenyang Li","target":"Author/Chenyang Li","line":147},{"title":"Author/Li Chenyang","target":"Author/Li Chenyang","line":148}],"metadata":{"id":"qian_natural_2022","type":"article-journal","title":"Natural Compound 2-Chloro-1,3-dimethoxy-5-methylbenzene, Isolated from <i>Hericium Erinaceus</i>, Inhibits Fungal Growth by Disrupting Membranes and Triggering Apoptosis","issued":{"date-parts":[[2022]]},"DOI":"10.1021/acs.jafc.2c01417","container-title":"Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry","abstract":"In this study, 2-chloro-1,3-dimethoxy-5-methylbenzene (CDM), a natural product with anti-Candida albicans activity, was discovered from the Hericium erinaceus mycelium. The minimum inhibitory concentration of CDM was 62.5 μg/mL. Moreover, structural analogues of CDM obtained from chemical synthesis were applied to explore the structure-activity relationship (SAR) of CDM against C. albicans. It was found that methoxy groups, halogen atoms (except fluorine atoms), and methoxy-meta-position methyl groups in the structure of CDM were the key active groups. Furthermore, we investigated the anti-C. albicans mechanism of CDM. Experiments suggested that CDM destroyed the cell membrane of C. albicans, including the cytoplasmic membrane and mitochondrial membrane, and caused the accumulation of reactive oxygen species and mitochondrial dysfunction, which ultimately led to apoptosis of C. albicans. In addition, CDM had no toxicity on human normal gastric mucosal epithelial cells exposed to a concentration of 125 μg/mL. Experiments showed that CDM reduced the damage of C. albicans to the visceral tissue of infected mice and improved the survival rate of mice. Our research provides a scientific basis for the discovery of effective and safe anti-C. albicans drugs from H. erinaceus.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Qian","given":"Zhang","literal":""},{"family":"Qian","given":"Zhang","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Mengxun","literal":""},{"family":"Mengxun","given":"Zhang","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Yingchao","literal":""},{"family":"Yingchao","given":"Wang","literal":""},{"family":"Tingting","given":"Zhen","literal":""},{"family":"Tingting","given":"Zhen","literal":""},{"family":"Roujuan","given":"Wang","literal":""},{"family":"Roujuan","given":"Wang","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Shuhong","literal":""},{"family":"Shuhong","given":"Wang","literal":""},{"family":"Du","given":"Yi","literal":""},{"family":"Yi","given":"Du","literal":""},{"family":"Ruirui","given":"Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Ruirui","given":"Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Peng","given":"Yi","literal":""},{"family":"Peng","given":"Yi","literal":""},{"family":"Song","given":"Yifan","literal":""},{"family":"Yifan","given":"Song","literal":""},{"family":"Zhi","given":"Yun-Shi","literal":""},{"family":"Yunshi","given":"Zhi","literal":""},{"family":"Song","given":"Xun","literal":""},{"family":"Xun","given":"Song","literal":""},{"family":"Guo","given":"Yaping","literal":""},{"family":"Yaping","given":"Guo","literal":""},{"family":"He","given":"Zhendan","literal":""},{"family":"Zhendan","given":"He","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Tie","literal":""},{"family":"Tie","given":"Chen","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"Chenyang","literal":""},{"family":"Chenyang","given":"Li","literal":""}],"citation-key":"qian_natural_2022","year":"2022","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Natural Compound 2-Chloro-1,3-dimethoxy-5-methylbenzene, Isolated from <i>Hericium Erinaceus</i>, Inhibits Fungal Growth by Disrupting Membranes and Triggering Apoptosis"],"author-links":["[[Author/Zhang Qian]]","[[Author/Zhang Qian]]","[[Author/Mengxun Zhang]]","[[Author/Zhang Mengxun]]","[[Author/Yingchao Wang]]","[[Author/Wang Yingchao]]","[[Author/Zhen Tingting]]","[[Author/Zhen Tingting]]","[[Author/Wang Roujuan]]","[[Author/Wang Roujuan]]","[[Author/Shuhong Wang]]","[[Author/Wang Shuhong]]","[[Author/Yi Du]]","[[Author/Du Yi]]","[[Author/Yu Ruirui]]","[[Author/Yu Ruirui]]","[[Author/Yi Peng]]","[[Author/Yi Peng]]","[[Author/Yifan Song]]","[[Author/Song Yifan]]","[[Author/Yun-Shi Zhi]]","[[Author/Zhi Yunshi]]","[[Author/Xun Song]]","[[Author/Song Xun]]","[[Author/Yaping Guo]]","[[Author/Guo Yaping]]","[[Author/Zhendan He]]","[[Author/He Zhendan]]","[[Author/Tie Chen]]","[[Author/Chen Tie]]","[[Author/Chenyang Li]]","[[Author/Li Chenyang]]"],"attachment":[],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1pmzu81","at":1774951888069}},"smart_blocks:Research/@qian_natural_2022.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06976079,-0.02360341,0.0530594,0.01252363,0.00266158,0.00126